#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about praise.\n"
"\n"
"Praise is a powerful parenting skill.\n"
"\n"
"If we praise our teens when they do something well, we will see them do more and more positive things!"
msgstr ""
"Kipindi cha leo ni kuhusu Kusifia.\n"
"\n"
"Kusifia ni ujuzi wenye nguvu katika malezi.\n"
"\n"
"Kama tutawasifia vijana wetu wanapofanya jambo vizuri, tutawaona wakifanya mambo mazuri zaidi na zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How will praise help you and your family? Tap play to find out!"
msgstr "Jinsi gani kusifia itasakusaidia na familia yako? Gusa cheza ili kujua!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Our topic today is about praise.\n"
"\n"
"It is good to praise our children when they've done good because when we do that, they will do more of that good behavior we want to see.\n"
"\n"
"And let's not forget to praise ourselves when we do good!"
msgstr ""
"Habari zenu?\n"
"\n"
"Kipindi chetu ya leo inahusu kusifia.\n"
"\n"
"Ni vizuri kuwasifia watoto wetu wanapofanya vizuri kwa sababu tunapofanya hivyo, watazidi kuifanya tabia nzuri tunayotaka kuiona.\n"
"\n"
"Na tusisahau pia kujisifia sisi wenyewe tunapofanya mazuri!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise is an easy way to build your teen’s confidence and strengthen your connection. It really works!"
msgstr "Kusifia ni njia rahisi kujenga kujiamini kwa kijana wako na kuimarisha uhusiano wenu. Inafanya kazi kweli!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise works, but it’s not always easy. Hear how @data.characters.media_female_2.name started using it at home"
msgstr "Kusifia kunafanya kazi, lakini siyo rahisi daima. Sikiliza jinsi @data.characters.media_female_2.name alivyoanza kuitumia nyumbani"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When we learnt about this praising thing I thought, “We were never praised for things as teenagers, so why should we start now?” But I got interested when I learnt what the benefits of praising could be.\n"
"\n"
"Right after the weekly workshop, I noticed my teen doing what they do every day: washing the dishes. And I said “Thank you for washing the dishes, my girl, it really makes me happy that you are helping out.” My teen was smiling and she even came to give me a hug, which she never does.\n"
"\n"
"This praising business is hard. I still forget sometimes or give praise at the same time as criticism. But praising really makes a difference. I never thought that a simple praise could make such a change in a person!"
msgstr ""
"Tulipojifunza kuhusu jambo hili la kusifu nilifikiri, “Hatukusifiwa kamwe kwa mambo tukiwa vijana, kwa hivyo kwa nini tuanze sasa?” Lakini nilipendezwa nilipojifunza faida za kusifu zingeweza kuwa nini.\n"
"\n"
"Mara tu baada ya warsha ya kila wiki, niliona kijana wangu akifanya kile anachofanya kila siku: kuosha vyombo. Na nikasema, \"Asante kwa kuosha vyombo, msichana wangu, inanifurahisha sana kwamba unasaidia.\" Kijana wangu alikuwa akitabasamu na hata alikuja kunikumbatia, jambo ambalo huwa hafanyi.\n"
"\n"
"Biashara hii ya kusifu ni ngumu. Bado ninasahau wakati mwingine au kutoa sifa wakati huo huo kama ukosoaji. Lakini kusifu kunafanya tofauti. Sikuwahi kufikiria kwamba sifa rahisi inaweza kufanya mabadiliko hayo kwa mtu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s reflect on our own experience with praise."
msgstr "Ebu tujikumbushe kwenye uzoefu wetu wa kusifia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Think about the last time someone thanked you, or said you did something great.\n"
"\n"
"How did it make you feel?"
msgstr ""
"Fikiria kuhusu mara ya mwisho mtu alipokushukuru, au alipokuambia umefanya kitu fulani kizuri sana.\n"
"\n"
"Ilikufanya ujisikieje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay"
msgstr "Sawa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We sometimes have to get used to being praised and praising others. That’s okay."
msgstr "Sisi wakati mwingine tunatakiwa kuzoea kusifiwa na kusifia wengine. Hiyo ni sawa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Happy"
msgstr "Furaha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Being praised often makes us feel happy."
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Kusifia mara kwa mara hutufanya kujihisi wenye furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Proud"
msgstr "Kujivunia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s great! Being praised often makes us feel proud."
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Kusifia mara kwa mara hutufanya kujihisi wenye furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Parents usually do not get thanked or praised enough.\n"
"\n"
"How does it make you feel when nobody says \"thank you\"?"
msgstr ""
"Mara nyingi Wazazi hawapewi shukrani au kusifia vya kutosha.\n"
"\n"
"Unajisikiaje pale ambapo hakuna mtu anakamia \"asante\"?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sad"
msgstr "Huzuni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Angry"
msgstr "Hasira"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tired"
msgstr "Kuchoka"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Your teen can feel this way too. That's what makes this week's parenting tool simple but important: Praise them for what they do right."
msgstr "Kijana wako anaweza pia kujisikia hivyo. Hicho ndicho kinachofanya nyenzo ya malezi ya wiki hii iwe rahisi lakini muhimu: Msifie anapofanya vizuri."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Here are some skills to help you praise your teens.\n"
"You can also praise other adults in your household, too. Notice how they respond!"
msgstr ""
"Huu hapa ni baadhi ya ujuzi wa kukusaidia kusifia vijana wako.\n"
"Unaweza pia kusifia watu wazima nyumbani kwako, vilevile. Gundua jins wanavyoitikia!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEE IT"
msgstr "ONA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look for anything your teen does that is helpful or good and praise them for it. They may not show it, but you will see them doing that good thing again. It will also reassure them that you notice and care."
msgstr "Tafuta kitu chochote anachofanya kijana wako kwa ajili ya kusaidia au kilicho kizuri na umsifie kwa kitu hicho. Anaweza asioneshe furaha yake, lakini utamwona akifanya tena kitu hicho kizuri. Pia itamthibitishia kuwa unatambua anachokifanya na unajali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SAY IT"
msgstr "SEMA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Be enthusiastic – really mean it when you say it!"
msgstr "Onyesha shauku – unaposema jambo, liseme kwa moyo wa dhati!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "REPEAT IT"
msgstr "RUDIA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Vidokezo zaidi\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It can be hard to think of reasons to praise your teen! Here are some ideas from other parents:"
msgstr "Wakati mwingine ni vigumu kufikiria kitu gani cha kumsifia kijana wako! Haya ni mawazo kutoka kwa wazazi wengine:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Thank you for...**\n"
"- Being kind to someone\n"
"- Cleaning your room\n"
"- Joining a family meal\n"
"- Greeting other family members\n"
"- Looking after your siblings\n"
"- Coming home on time\n"
"- Showing thoughtfulness\n"
"- Saying 'please' or 'thank you'\n"
"- Going to school on time\n"
"- Doing chores or schoolwork"
msgstr ""
"**Asante kwa...**\n"
"- Kuwa mkarimu kwa mtu fulani\n"
"- Kusafisha chumba chako\n"
"- Kujiunga katika chakula cha familia\n"
"- Kusalimia wanafamilia wengine\n"
"- Kuwaangalia wadogo zako\n"
"- Kurudi nyumbani kwa wakati\n"
"- Kuonyesha unafikiria\n"
"- Kusema “tafadhali” au “asante”\n"
"- Kwenda shule kwa wakati\n"
"- Kufanya kazi za nyumbani au kazi za shule"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you praise your teen once a day this week?"
msgstr "Unaweza kumsifia kijana wako mara moja kwa siku kwa wiki hii?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Parents who practise praise at home get better results!"
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Wazazi wanaofanya zoezi la kusifia nyumbani wanapata Matokeo mazuri zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Nafikiri hivyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try praising your teen for something simple at first, like looking after their siblings or going to school."
msgstr "Unaweza kufanya! Jaribu kumsifia kijana wako kwa kitu rahisi mwanzoni, kwa kuwaangalia wdago zake a kwa kwenda shule."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. With time, giving praise will become easier. Try to praise yourself for something first, like \"Good job using @global.app_name. It shows you care.\""
msgstr "Hiyo ni sawa. Baada ya muda, kusifia itakuwa rahisi zaidi. Jaribu kujisifia mwenyewe kwa kitu flani kwanza, kama \"Kazi nzuri @global.app_name. Huonesha unajari\"."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, praise is a powerful tool. The more attention you give to positive behaviour, the more positive behaviour you will see."
msgstr "Kumbuka, kusifia ni nyenzo yenye nguvu. Kadri unavyoweka umakini zaidi kwenye tabia chanya, ndivyo utakavyoona zaidi tabia chanya."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear from @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name on how it feels to get praise from her mother"
msgstr "Sikia kutoka @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name jinsi anavyojisikia aliposifiwa na mama yake"

